value.0: This chest should never be in an accessable area by the PCs!

This crystal is ground to a pulp and placed in a bowl of water to produce a gas, which if inhaled can alter's one's perception of time and increase their ability to move extremely quick.

(Epic Blinding Speed)

Because of the crystal's magical nature, it can only be used once.
This strange looking crystal glows with magic, but you don't know what it does exactly.
